        'decision_prompt'      => 'As Master, describe your complete emergency response. Address: (1) your immediate crisis priorities and command structure, (2) fire containment verification and engineering damage control plan, (3) passenger safety management including the trapped elevator passengers, crowd control, and injury response, (4) your assessment of whether to prepare for abandonment vs. await power restoration, and (5) coordination with the Coast Guard and assisting vessels.',
